  <brief_title>Aquatic Exercises for Patients With Chronic Low Back Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Aquatic Exercises Versus Aquatic Exercises Associated to Deep Water-running for Patients With Chronic Low Back Pain: Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
